 <name>WatchFlower</name>
 <summary>WatchFlower helps you read and plot datas from your Xiaomi "Flower Care" devices!</summary>
 <description>
   <p>
   WatchFlower is a small application to help you read and plot datas from your
   Xiaomi "Flower Care" devices. It works with all versions of the device, and
   doesn't require GPS or other any other private datas from you.
   </p>
 </description>
